      "text": "2 (1) An individual must be appointed as the Registrar of Passenger Transportation under subsection (2). (2) The registrar and the officers and employees necessary to carry out the powers, functions and duties of the registrar are to be appointed in accordance with the Public Service Act. (3) The registrar has the powers conferred, and must perform the duties imposed, on the registrar under this Act.",
